sentences.english: Each air waybill has three originals and at least 6 copies.
sentences.chinese: 每份空運運單有三份正本以及至少六份副本。

sentences.english: Please fill in the luggage consignment notes and labels.
sentences.chinese: 請填寫行李託運單和貨籤。

sentences.english: Airport Customs shall confirm the electronic data of waybill recorded by the airline company.
sentences.chinese: 航空公司錄入運單電子數據，機場海關進行確認。

sentences.english: You should send one copy of the shipping documents to the port of destination together with the shipment.
sentences.chinese: 裝船同時貴方應將貨運單據副本寄送目的港。

sentences.english: Your ticket, boarding pass and luggage check.
sentences.chinese: 您的票，登機卡和行李託運單。

sentences.english: OK. Please fill the waybill first.
Without original HAWB , customs will not release cargo to the cnee.
sentences.chinese: 沒有原始分空運單，海關將不對收貨人放行貨物。

sentences.english: We need master AWB please send to us.
sentences.chinese: 我們需要主運單，請發送給我們。

sentences.english: I didn't realize I should have given it to you as soon as it arrived.
sentences.chinese: 我底子出有唸到貨運單一到就應當給你收去。

sentences.english: International Railway Bill can be used in land bridge transport.
sentences.chinese: 國際鐵路貨運單可以用於大陸橋運輸。
